title: Here Are a Few Different Ways To Sell Your House (Hour 3)
description:
Dave Ramsey & Dr. John Delony discuss:

The logistics of selling a house,

What to do with an annuity,

Pausing baby step 2 to set up a "strike fund",

Pre-planned funeral arrangements.
